  "text": "where Q is N r × N r complex orthogonal matrix, R is N t × N r complex upper triangular matrix with positive diagonal elements. The QR decomposition is of critical importance in many MIMO detection algorithms to reduce the complexity of receivers and to get better decoding results [CITATION_1] .",
